{"tid":1265250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀區選強攻三聖有重大陰謀，屯門人要拯救香港！","createTime":"2019-06-29T05:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:22:08.000Z","uid":92198,"like":270,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"dadfb210ea7cd41f673a69ec55826bebcd98cd5d","tid":1265250,"uid":92198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"小弟住咗三聖二十幾年，都係蘇炤成條仆街霸住個位，點知屌你老味，今年葉劉竟然空降參選，仲要租咗黃金海岸單位住。葉劉從來離地到仆街，參選當然唔係為服務居民，而係劍指超區啦，而如果佢當選超區，就自然可以同中央講自己有民意基礎，可以選特首。條友係咩料大家03年都見過，隨時係689加777，23條重臨應該毫無懸念。<br />\n<br />\n蘇炤成條友自區議會選舉成立以來一直連任至今，都幾撚癡線，而葉劉同蘇炤成都係新民黨，更恐怖嘅係，葉劉應該仲可以吸多啲中產票，都咪話唔驚。大家不如集思廣益，睇下點可以令葉劉落選啦。<br />\n<br />\n相關資料：<br />\n三聖選區：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnMU0Dp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnMU0Dp.png&h=517da777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【政壇諸事町】傳擬租住黃金海岸備戰區選  葉劉：私隱不便透露<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/308874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F308874&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=10db5a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/308874</a>"},{"pid":"e37b1437ff97849e91dbb8c4ccc959417e7d5621","tid":1265250,"uid":173849,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"條友想選超區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d65e16d1df92b16c6767aa2d24b6298e829fa","tid":1265250,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d278ab5a1e2831aba3a9ef1d478840c06af2e4c","tid":1265250,"uid":183576,"like":5,"dislike":85,"score":-80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"由佢上啦，阻唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三聖呢啲區我地郁唔起"},{"pid":"690fe6a7c3b116d6c327a97c53b7c31f01d718b7","tid":1265250,"uid":92198,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"